al spectral embedding\n$\\xcal(R)\\hookrightarrow\\scal(R(T))$ which makes $\\xcal(R)$ a spectral retract\nof $\\scal(R(T))$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2017 17:35:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-30"}
