, or for a system with a high transmit power, the\nimpact of applying a distortion-aware design is significant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2017 19:33:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2017 22:15:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2017 09:09:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 11 Aug 2017 15:23:58 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 16:20:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
