s perpendicular diffusion and reduces\nparallel diffusion; the parallel mfp varies with rigidity $(P)$ as $P^{.33}$,\nand the perpendicular mfp is weakly dependent on $P$; the mfps are weakly\ninfluenced by the choice of long wavelength power spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2017 05:36:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Aug 2017 01:29:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-18"}
