de mucin glycans and are not degradable by any of the paired\norganisms alone. Taken together, these findings provide further insight into\nthe inter-microbial communications of the HGM as well as into host-HGM\ninteractions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2017 15:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-31"}
